      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. NO CHARGE had been racing well prior to her last start seventh at this track following a Grade 5 win three back with a third placing. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. 8. SUPER TONE ran below best last time finishing sixth (19.47) over 350m at Healesville from Box 8. Goes very well from this draw with seven wins and four minor placings from 17 starts. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. 3. TERRORISING TOM is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 23.45 beating Scotch Fever. Should be in this for a long way. 4. SHE'S SALTY won as punters’ elect last time – cannot be taken lightly.\",\"runners\":[2,8,3,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
